column5: anyone ever been to obatanga provincial park? i have and am just looking for a little more information about fishing in the area, i've only fished burnfield and cotton lakes....... any other good lakes aaround the area?
I've fished Fungus just before you get there. Watch for sanctuary regs though.
lol well come on, let the information flow.... wheres the best 'eye lake around there? and how do i get to it
Hey  When are you leaving?  I gots some ideas for you.
hey, well im supposed to be going at the end of the month. went there the same time 2 years ago and it was great!
